[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0098","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0433","title":"XFree86 X11R6 startx 命令符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"XFree86 的 startx 命令存在符号链接（symlink）漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在关键目录中创建符号链接文件，利用 startx 脚本以提升的权限写入或覆盖受限文件，从而可能实现本地权限提升或造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 X11R6 3.3.3 及之前版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0433"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.133","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至 4.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 startx 的符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，建议使用 xinit 替代 startx 启动 X 会话，或确保 /tmp 目录以 nosuid、noexec 选项挂载，并启用 sticky bit（chmod +t /tmp）防止符号链接攻击。现代 Linux 发行版应迁移至 Xorg 替代 XFree86。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0433","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0433","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0433.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vfv2-37hx-mr4p/GHSA-vfv2-37hx-mr4p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0433.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990331.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0098.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0155","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0155.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0482","title":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核 TSS 处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核的 TSS（任务状态段）处理逻辑存在缺陷，本地攻击者可通过运行 crashme 程序触发内核崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞源于内核在 TSS 切换时未正确处理异常状态，攻击者无需特殊权限即可利用，影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，建议升级至更高版本修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0482"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.517","remediation":"立即升级到 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本；若无法升级，请从 OpenBSD 官方 errata 页面下载并应用 2.4 内核补丁 019（针对 crashme 程序导致的 TSS 处理崩溃），该补丁以 unified diff 格式提供，按补丁内说明重新编译内核后重启即可。作为临时缓解措施，可限制本地用户登录或禁用 crashme 等压力测试工具的运行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7557"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0155.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0076","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0076.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0424","title":"Netscape Communicator 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.5 中集成的 talkback 崩溃报告组件存在任意文件写入漏洞。当目标用户的 Netscape 浏览器发生崩溃时，talkback 进程会以该用户权限执行文件写入操作，同一系统上的本地攻击者可利用此机制覆盖受害用户的任意文件，造成数据破坏或信息泄露。攻击依赖本地访问且需用户浏览器崩溃触发，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。建议升级软件或禁用 talkback 组件。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0424"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.030","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.51 及以上版本即可修复此漏洞；若无法升级，可删除或重命名 talkback 可执行文件（通常位于 Netscape 安装目录下的 `talkback` 文件）以禁用崩溃报告功能。作为临时缓解措施，确保 `/tmp` 目录设置粘滞位（chmod +t /tmp），防止非所有者删除或覆盖文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0424"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0076.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0078","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0078.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0425","title":"Netscape Communicator talkback 本地进程终止漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.5 浏览器的 \"talkback\" 崩溃报告功能存在本地权限滥用漏洞。当一位用户的 Netscape 程序崩溃时，talkback 组件未能正确隔离进程间操作权限，允许同一系统上的本地攻击者利用该机制向任意其他用户的进程发送终止信号，导致非授权进程被终止。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限且目标用户需运行易受攻击的 Netscape 版本，造成拒绝服务或关键服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0425"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.143","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.6 及以上版本可修复此漏洞。对于无法升级的环境，建议禁用 talkback 功能：删除或重命名 Netscape 安装目录下的 talkback 可执行文件，或通过配置文件禁用 crash reporter 组件。鉴于 Netscape 浏览器已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至 Firefox 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0425","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0425","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0425.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7gf5-w5c8-cpr2/GHSA-7gf5-w5c8-cpr2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0425.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82494/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000580.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1533f373-1dea-4090-b2f5-07632a1ff6e8.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0078.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0072","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0072.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0420","title":"BSD umapfs 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"umapfs（用户映射文件系统）存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过恶意构造的 mount_umap 程序修改自身用户标识符（UID），从而绕过系统权限检查获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响使用 umapfs 的 UNIX 系统，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0420"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.550","remediation":"立即移除 mount_umap 程序的 setuid-root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mount_umap），如不使用 umapfs 文件系统可直接卸载该组件。联系操作系统厂商确认是否有对应安全补丁，升级到已修复 umapfs 漏洞的版本。在不影响业务的前提下，禁用 umapfs 内核模块支持以防止恶意加载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0420"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0072.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0074","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0074.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0422","title":"NetBSD mount noexec 标志绕过漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.3 的 mount 命令存在安全绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过挂载特定的文件系统绕过 \"noexec\" 标志限制，在标记为禁止执行的文件系统上执行任意程序。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.3.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级至 NetBSD 1.4 及以上版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0422"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.797","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复 mount 命令忽略 noexec 标志的问题。如无法立即升级，可在 /etc/fstab 中对敏感分区额外设置 nosuid 标志并限制本地用户登录，降低绕过执行的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0422"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0074.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0126","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0126.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0462","title":"Linux Perl suidperl 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Perl 中的 suidperl 组件在解析 setuid 脚本时未检查文件系统的 nosuid 挂载选项，本地攻击者可将特制 setuid Perl 脚本放置于可挂载文件系统（如 CD-ROM 或软盘）上，通过诱使目标系统挂载并执行该脚本触发漏洞。成功利用后可获取 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 SUSE Linux 等多个发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0462"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.813","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004_04 或更高版本，该版本已修复 suidperl 对 nosuid 挂载选项的检查逻辑。作为临时缓解措施，执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl` 移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限位，并将所有可移动文件系统（如 CD-ROM、软盘）以 `nosuid` 选项挂载，防止攻击者通过可移动介质提权至 root。长期建议迁移至 suidperl 已被彻底移除的 Perl 5.26+ 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/339"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0126.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0073","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0073.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0421","title":"Slackware Linux 安装后重启root账户未授权登录漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 3.6 系统在安装后首次重启过程中存在身份认证绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可在系统启动阶段利用 root 账号无需密码直接登录，从而获得系统最高权限。该漏洞源于安装程序在初次重启时未正确设置 root 账户密码，攻击条件简单，无需任何身份凭证即可完全控制目标系统。影响范围包括 Slackware 3.6 及可能的相关版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0421"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-17","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装完成后首次重启前，务必使用 passwd root 命令为 root 账户设置强密码。升级到 Slackware Linux 3.6 以上版本，新版本在安装流程中强制要求设置 root 密码。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inittab 中配置单用户模式需要密码认证，并检查 /etc/shadow 确保 root 密码字段非空。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/981","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/338"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0073.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0621","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0621.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0385","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 LDAP Bind 函数缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 目录服务的 LDAP Bind 函数存在未检查的缓冲区，远程攻击者可发送特制的畸形 Bind 请求导致缓冲区溢出，造成 Exchange 目录服务崩溃（拒绝服务），或在特定条件下通过经典缓冲区溢出技术执行任意代码。攻击无法意外触发，需要主动发送恶意 LDAP 请求。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0385"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-16","updated":"2003-03-10","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 官方安全公告 MS99-009 提供的补丁，或禁用 Exchange 目录服务中的 LDAP 支持，或在网络防火墙上过滤发往 TCP 端口 389 的入站数据包以降低外部攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:17:10.890517061+00:00","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-009","https://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;en-us;221989"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0621.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0037","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0382","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 屏幕保护程序权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 中的屏幕保护程序在安全上下文切换时未正确验证权限变更，导致本地攻击者可通过物理访问终端或诱导系统进入屏保状态触发该漏洞，以提升后的权限执行任意程序。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 NT 3.5.1 的多个 Service Pack 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0382"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.647","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统（Windows NT 4.0/3.5.1 已于 2004 年停止支持，不再提供安全更新）。如无法升级，可在组策略编辑器（gpedit.msc）中启用「屏幕保护程序超时锁定」策略，并将屏幕保护程序启动等待时间设为不超过 15 分钟，同时确保所有用户账户均设有强密码，限制非授权用户的本地登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0382","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0382.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3/GHSA-9h86-j86m-7fx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0382.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--284f3c9d-c5aa-4a6f-9d77-395fb3b2fa10.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0062","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0062.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0415","title":"Cisco 7xx系列路由器HTTP服务默认开启漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器（3.2 至 4.2 版本）的 HTTP 服务器默认开启，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 HTTP 接口访问路由器管理页面，进而修改路由器配置，造成网络服务中断或流量劫持。该漏洞影响 Cisco 700 系列路由器，攻击者只需知道路由器 IP 地址即可利用，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0415"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.933","remediation":"升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 IOS 至 4.2 以上版本，或通过命令行执行 `no http-server` 禁用 HTTP 管理服务，并在访问控制列表中限制仅允许可信管理 IP 访问路由器管理端口。若无法升级，建议在边界防火墙上阻断对路由器 TCP 80 端口的公网访问。Cisco 已在后续版本中将 HTTP 服务默认关闭。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-034.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/7xxconn-pub.shtml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0415.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0415","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0415.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gx7p-m72r-4gq2/GHSA-gx7p-m72r-4gq2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82498/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0415.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0062.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0064","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0064.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0416","title":"Cisco 700系列路由器 Telnet TCP连接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 Telnet 端口（默认 23/TCP）建立 TCP 连接，触发路由器系统重新加载，导致设备暂时不可用。该漏洞影响 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。受影响的 Cisco 7xx 设备因无法正确处理 Telnet 端口上的 TCP 连接请求，导致设备崩溃重启，造成网络服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0416"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.073","remediation":"建议升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器至最新固件版本（如 IOS 11.3(5) 或更高），并在路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL）限制 Telnet 端口的源 IP 范围，仅允许受信任的管理主机连接。如业务允许，建议禁用 Telnet 服务，改用 SSH 进行远程管理。对于已停产的 7xx 系列设备，建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Cisco 路由器型号。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-034.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/7xxconn-pub.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19919","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0416.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0416","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0416.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3w3-x7jr-4c3v/GHSA-p3w3-x7jr-4c3v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0416.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0064.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0065","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0065.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0417","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 procfs 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 的 procfs（进程文件系统）存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 /proc 文件系统发送特制的请求或操作，触发系统内核崩溃或资源耗尽，导致目标系统不可用。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地用户身份才能利用，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0417"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-09","updated":"1999-03-09","remediation":"立即安装 Sun（现 Oracle）针对 Solaris 7 64-bit 系统发布的 procfs 补丁（Solaris 7 推荐补丁集 106541-xx，含 procfs 修复）。若无法升级系统，可将 /proc 文件系统挂载选项设置为 nosuid 并限制非 root 用户对 /proc 的访问权限，以缓解本地拒绝服务攻击。建议将已 EOL 的 Solaris 7 升级至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11 或更新版本，从根本上解决此问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19326","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0417","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0417.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pc9-mc38-6cmq/GHSA-9pc9-mc38-6cmq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0417.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f71e3200-5b60-40de-a215-2cc104f46dcc.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0065.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0065.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0065.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1254","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 ICMP重定向消息拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 操作系统内核网络协议栈在处理 ICMP（Internet Control Message Protocol）重定向消息时存在设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过伪造路由器发送的 ICMP 重定向报文，欺骗目标系统修改其路由表条目，将网络流量重定向至恶意路径，导致目标主机网络连接中断，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 等早期版本，攻击者无需任何认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1254"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.813","remediation":"Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 均已终止支持且不再有安全更新，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+ 等受支持版本。如在旧系统上需临时缓解，可将注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\EnableICMPRedirect` 设为 `0` 以禁用 ICMP 重定向处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92099515709467&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1947","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1254","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72gc-hjc8-g277/GHSA-72gc-hjc8-g277.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87822/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000568.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1087","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1087.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1371","title":"Sun Solaris /usr/bin/write 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 及 2.7 系统中的 /usr/bin/write 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向终端名称参数传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统最高权限。该漏洞为本地提权漏洞，攻击者需拥有本地账户才能利用，影响 Solaris 2.6 和 2.7 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1371"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.847","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 Solaris 2.6 和 7，Oracle 不再提供安全补丁。建议立即升级到受支持的 Solaris 11 或更高版本；如无法升级，可执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/write` 移除 setuid 位以缓解提权风险，或使用 `chmod 0 /usr/bin/write` 完全禁用该命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92100752221493&w=2","http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/5ZP0O1P35O.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7546","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/256"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1087.toml"}]